#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Vihāravagga"
msgstr "2. Meditation"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Paṭhamaparisuddhasutta"
msgstr "16. Purified (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.16:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.16:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā parisuddhā pariyodātā anaṅgaṇā vigatūpakkilesā "
"anuppannā uppajjanti, nāññatra tathāgatassa pātubhāvā arahato "
"sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these eight things don’t arise to be purified, bright, "
"flawless, and rid of imperfections except when a Realized One, a perfected "
"one, a fully awakened Buddha has appeared."

msgctxt "sn45.16:1.3"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "sn45.16:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"They are: right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right "
"livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.16:1.5"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā parisuddhā pariyodātā anaṅgaṇā "
"vigatūpakkilesā anuppannā uppajjanti, nāññatra tathāgatassa pātubhāvā "
"arahato sammāsambuddhassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These eight things don’t arise to be purified, bright, flawless, and rid of "
"imperfections except when a Realized One, a perfected one, a fully awakened "
"Buddha has appeared.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.16:1.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
